          "sourceFilename": "1979_find_greatest_common_divisor_of_array.rs",
          "code": "impl Solution {\n    pub fn find_gcd(nums: Vec<i32>) -> i32 {\n        let (&first, rest) = nums.split_first().unwrap();\n        let mut max = first;\n        let mut min = first;\n        for &n in rest {\n            max = max.max(n);\n            min = min.min(n);\n        }\n        while min != 0 {\n            (max, min) = (min, max % min)\n        }\n        max\n    }\n}\n\nstruct Solution {}\n",
